{"tid":1365144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請置頂 727物資站","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T17:28:10.000Z","uid":45046,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3fea6d1afee15e6e96431461d6e3004bc298d15a","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:18:26.000Z","msg":"我係早幾日出左個post大家可以入去睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1352131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1352131</a><br />\n根據警方出左反對通知書 <br />\n當日只要多過3個人就有機會被告非法集結<br />\n同警方多次違法沒收物資站嘅個人財產<br />\n仲有元朗當日太多不確定因素 <br />\n建立物資站同溝通嘅難道都大大提升<br />\n我係上個post有同其他義士搞左個gp<br />\n大約左20-30人 我地認為用百佳惠康手推車<br />\n做流動物資站係可行 行動上會更be water<br />\n我地都有不少人有上前線嘅經驗 <br />\n我地清楚明白前線需要咩物資同裝備<br />\n但因為我地係建立初期<br />\n好多人手資源上太多不足<br />\n我地需要大家嘅幫手 捐助物資 工具<br />\n需要義載車手協助運送物資 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地當日會帶上寫有平字嘅安全帽<br />\n象徵我地係平民物資站義工<br />\n(如果有人反對就唔會帶)</span><br />\n我地係到發出聲明 我地只係義工<br />\n只係會接收 處理 派發物資 唔會做採購<br />\n所以絕不接受現金捐助<br />\n我地希望大家可以係元朗區租定手推車<br />\n如果有鎖鏈 可以先鎖係街邊備用<br />\n我地需要嘅物資係有好多<br />\n強力電筒 盾牌 長於1米嘅雨傘 豬咀 濾咀 各大小嘅乾淨舊衫 防割手套 大聲公 醫療用品等<br />\n今次唔會好似上一次咁會有gear提供 <br />\n到時我地會係連登同tg報告我嘅嘅位置 <br />\n都會派人去前線派發物資<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"be519e0752f2cabdb9818fca552628803846c0b2","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:18:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef8d719bbdab16bc851074b4a11bd01fd7b922fe","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42daa1eec884d1fe25dc7b0d1f0332fcc193f3e1","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:25:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1de4c49dcf0fe6de9c98fb7a06b859866c38946a","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1d7d122ba37e32c26cbbb87a07ada14bf08cb80","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:31:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cc7db5fa3cecf6acb2427caef93cac2ffcf1228","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b253ead8c0ea595638cf55a2bf37b2d84b4e712","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e6f278b0aba19ed226adcefb562928d875bc917","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:32:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9871ef9296176cfd1c0a6bcbc17db42bb99b6168","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"cd441f936e6fd7a851a34fa430aa075c22809f17","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:32:58.000Z","msg":"想幫手既都可以留低tg"},{"pid":"c682598ce50dc80dc2191a895686709b907777a4","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30b7d505ee99ca917ccfd428bdf334615bd115c5","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:33:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cf9a47d8aea2fdd34639fb345ef0a6da6765bd61","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:33:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d47e179ebe6a5aaec891b18acf5107926bd3bf3","tid":1365144,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"留tg"},{"pid":"3b9a7475a7cdbc9ab96e71cb4486dc4d62056bf3","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ebdcd001d1c08c3374525d6472e44c70af26a6b","tid":1365144,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d29fcc04c0e2484751c9b594764440d0317ca7bb","tid":1365144,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f559075f24ef7aba1f2ced7ee04bc4d03c899ad6","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d47e179ebe6a5aaec891b18acf5107926bd3bf3","tid":1365144,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"留tg"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:40.000Z","msg":"你想幫手就留低tg 我聯絡你"},{"pid":"48622eccbf4a891f96295663faabd6f75aedc7bc","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f648fafeaf1c027483d119736289bfff83beecf7","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c8cbcc16c6cfe8afdd4b941c7b52672d857b38","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f6e5c9a9767fbe085fc4cf4c26e4b8140c189bb6","tid":1365144,"uid":222633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fea3dc45787fb9313018a93ccfd5742584a88581","tid":1365144,"uid":45046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:35:31.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2287bbe35a29aa3bdd391e42ef951e2abc64f4ab","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db560cc8871b797cb2ede2815edb57b1f0f3903d","tid":1365144,"uid":135053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply